title: december 3: crash into mars
description:
Today on 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about a crash, not a stock market crash or a car crash, but a spacecraft crash on Mars. Then, she talks about the release of a modern music phenomena. Join this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
